{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1111,"text":"Everyone, please think\nof your biggest personal goal."},{"time":4857,"text":"For real -- you can take a second.\nYou've got to feel this to learn it."},{"time":8429,"text":"Take a few seconds and think\nof your personal biggest goal, okay?"},{"time":12167,"text":"Imagine deciding right now\nthat you're going to do it."},{"time":14872,"text":"Imagine telling someone that you\nmeet today what you're going to do."},{"time":18165,"text":"Imagine their congratulations,"},{"time":20424,"text":"and their high image of you."},{"time":22000,"text":"Doesn't it feel good to say it out loud?"},{"time":24373,"text":"Don't you feel one step closer already,"},{"time":26863,"text":"like it's already becoming\npart of your identity?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":29341,"text":"Well, bad news: you should\nhave kept your mouth shut,"},{"time":33361,"text":"because that good feeling"},{"time":34814,"text":"now will make you less likely to do it."},{"time":37495,"text":"The repeated psychology tests have proven"},{"time":39845,"text":"that telling someone your goal\nmakes it less likely to happen."},{"time":44106,"text":"Any time you have a goal,"},{"time":45435,"text":"there are some steps that need to be done,"},{"time":47483,"text":"some work that needs to be done\nin order to achieve it."},{"time":50088,"text":"Ideally you would not be satisfied\nuntil you'd actually done the work."},{"time":53408,"text":"But when you tell someone your goal\nand they acknowledge it,"},{"time":56304,"text":"psychologists have found\nthat it's called a \"social reality.\""},{"time":59231,"text":"The mind is kind of tricked\ninto feeling that it's already done."},{"time":62265,"text":"And then because you've felt\nthat satisfaction,"},{"time":64544,"text":"you're less motivated to do\nthe actual hard work necessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67516,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68849,"text":"So this goes against conventional wisdom"},{"time":70905,"text":"that we should tell our friends\nour goals, right?"},{"time":73318,"text":"So they hold us to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75867,"text":"So, let's look at the proof."},{"time":78000,"text":"1926: Kurt Lewin,\nfounder of social psychology,"},{"time":80850,"text":"called this \"substitution.\""},{"time":82354,"text":"1933: Wera Mahler found\nwhen it was acknowledged by others,"},{"time":85743,"text":"it felt real in the mind."},{"time":87482,"text":"1982, Peter Gollwitzer\nwrote a whole book about this,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and in 2009,"},{"time":91567,"text":"he did some new tests that were published."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94138,"text":"It goes like this:"},{"time":95630,"text":"163 people across four separate tests."},{"time":99216,"text":"Everyone wrote down their personal goal."},{"time":101534,"text":"Then half of them announced\ntheir commitment to this goal to the room,"},{"time":105445,"text":"and half didn't."},{"time":107500,"text":"Then everyone was given 45 minutes of work"},{"time":109555,"text":"that would directly lead them\ntowards their goal,"},{"time":111874,"text":"but they were told\nthat they could stop at any time."},{"time":114342,"text":"Now, those who kept their mouths shut"},{"time":116249,"text":"worked the entire 45 minutes on average,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and when asked afterward,"},{"time":120561,"text":"said that they felt\nthat they had a long way to go still"},{"time":123249,"text":"to achieve their goal."},{"time":124426,"text":"But those who had announced it"},{"time":126000,"text":"quit after only 33 minutes, on average,"},{"time":128866,"text":"and when asked afterward,"},{"time":130620,"text":"said that they felt much closer\nto achieving their goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133355,"text":"So if this is true, what can we do?"},{"time":136639,"text":"Well, you could resist the temptation\nto announce your goal."},{"time":141000,"text":"You can delay the gratification\nthat the social acknowledgment brings,"},{"time":145308,"text":"and you can understand that your mind\nmistakes the talking for the doing."},{"time":149699,"text":"But if you do need\nto talk about something,"},{"time":152072,"text":"you can state it in a way\nthat gives you no satisfaction,"},{"time":156443,"text":"such as, \"I really want\nto run this marathon,"},{"time":158586,"text":"so I need to train five times a week"},{"time":160340,"text":"and kick my ass if I don't, okay?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":162710,"text":"So audience, next time you're\ntempted to tell someone your goal,"},{"time":165835,"text":"what will you say?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":167009,"text":"(Silence)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168034,"text":"Exactly! Well done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169310,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}